data.title: Etoo - Google Search
data.meta_description:
etoo - Google Search - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Samuel Eto'o is a retired Cameroonian professional footballer who played as a striker. He is considered one of the greatest African footballers of all time. Some key facts:

- He played for many top European clubs including Barcelona, Inter Milan, Chelsea, and Everton. 

- With Barcelona, he won 3 Champions League titles and 2 La Liga titles. 

- He also won the Champions League and multiple domestic titles with Inter Milan.

- Eto'o was named African Player of the Year 4 times, won multiple domestic awards, and was named in the FIFA 100 list of the world's greatest living players.
